YQLAutoTagger is a script that uses Yahoo's Term Extraction service to 
analyse a form field and automatically fill a "tags" field with keywords 
when the user moves away from the field. 

Check out the <a href="http://wiki.github.com/codepo8/YQLAutoTagger">wiki</a> for documentation or see a demo at: http://isithackday.com/demos/yqlautotagger.html

Enjoy, Chris.